On the evening of February 4, several vehicles collided and caught fire near Wangcheng Toll Station in Hunan Province on Xuguang Expressway.
According to the local emergency department, firefighters and highway traffic police have arrived at the scene to deal with the situation. The current casualties are unknown. In the video posted by netizens, several large trucks and small cars were crowded together, the fire was blazing, and thick smoke was billowing at the scene.
